{"tid":1162617,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中美貿易戰】戰火蔓延到影視圈！ 中國劇拍美國生活遭撤檔","createTime":"2019-05-20T03:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T04:12:12.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"58c57e888e5911d0f6b37b5b43500a23fe8841dc","tid":1162617,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T03:35:48.000Z","msg":"垃圾蘋果日報點解唔用內地啊？平時講中港關係就用內地，一到講中美關係就用中國，擺明有政治目的<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190519/large/1558248226_7929.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190519%2Flarge%2F1558248226_7929.jpg&h=e06f2757&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中美貿易戰越演越烈，中方除了枱面上的貿易限縮，也悄悄在廣電播放政策上勒緊韁繩。除了早前央視一連4日改播放反美愛國劇集外，原定今天（19日）播出的新劇《帶着爸爸去留學》，疑因涉及中美生活、文化的探討，加上有大量美國場景，臨時遭撤檔，由Angelababy主演的《我的真朋友》頂上。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：「特朗普馬桶刷」淘寶爆紅　海外有售<br />\n<br />\n《帶着爸爸去留學》班底集結孫紅雷、辛芷蕾、劉敏濤等實力派演員，又是東方衞視、浙江衞視、騰訊視頻、愛奇藝、優酷等5大平台聯合播放，卻突然遭撤檔，微博用戶@微博電視劇原本寫明，《帶着爸爸去留學》是由於中美貿易戰將劇集撤檔，之後又刪掉相關字句。據指，該劇講述留學美國陪讀生活，被認定「不合時宜」。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n有網民在微博嘆道「只能說又一部在國家政治下犧牲的電視劇，此舉何嘗不是對於那些辛苦付出的影視行業從業人員勞動成果的不尊重呢？」「好氣啊&hellip;&hellip;期待了那麼久了&hellip;&hellip;說撤就撤了&hellip;&hellip;​」「看來在米（美）國拍的都不行了。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：借出22年拒續約華收回加州兩熊貓<br />\n<br />\n李易峰、江疏影主演的《我在北京等你》，以及電視劇版《北京遇上西雅圖》都有不少涉及美國的元素，都可能因中美貿易戰受到影響；而李晨主演的《七日生》恰好播完大結局，逃過被審查命運。<br />\n<br />\n央視早於16日晚間延遲播出亞洲影視周紅毯典禮，播放《英雄兒女》、《上甘嶺》、《奇襲》等抗美援朝的戰爭片，對於這樣「政治正確」的調整，電視頻道表示：「特殊的情況下確實是會做一些臨時的撤片和換片，我們是在用電影這樣一種藝術作品，呼應當下的時代。」而民間也不乏支持力量，「台獨剋星」黃安也在微博信心喊話：「加油！中國隊，加油！美國隊，漏油！ 」<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果新聞網》"},{"pid":"8f3a105bd4ca1b0edc634af17990d9004ae3ad31","tid":1162617,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T03:37:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190519/59617692?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190519%2F59617692%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ15hvY2R4XAiH6OvuWOSnKsk%3D&h=5474c0ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190519%2F59617692%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=4f7aeed4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190519/59617692?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"356dfc0cb195a481c26a41bb9326a4a76da769c9","tid":1162617,"uid":64290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T03:38:01.000Z","msg":"收返兩隻熊貓洩憤<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b3f91782c577c18cbbf2cc307839898d6f1cb68","tid":1162617,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T03:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c994f12ed7e10677144dabe5c1b9aeb90c4d35","tid":1162617,"uid":54437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T04:23:08.000Z","msg":"AVG4 上遲一個月應該就冇得喺中國播<br />\n<br />\n美國隊長<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678fcaf7513d288d6c5928d71eb1891511c01a46","tid":1162617,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:09:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba4490ef83322186d78bda9792a935e7bcb20588","tid":1162617,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T04:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}